reviewText: Not as much to it as I thought there would be. I bought it used for a very good price so I am not totally disappointed. Good information.
Blessed many people with the truth and promise of God

People gave their testimonies how they were healed of incurable diseases. Pat Robertson then commented on the importance of forgiveness or repentance or what ever issue was brought up about healing. I found this to be excellent and I enjoyed it immensely. I just wish Pat could have spoken longer about healing from his standpoint.
